# 🎨 Color Guessing Game

A fun and interactive web-based game where players match colors visually. Test your color perception skills and see how many you can guess correctly!

[![Live Demo](https://img.shields.io/badge/demo-live-green?style=for-the-badge)](https://your-demolink.com)

![Game Screenshot](/screenshot.png) <!-- Add actual screenshot path -->

## 🌟 Features

- **Visual Color Matching**: Guess colors without hex codes
- **Dynamic Scoring System**: Track your correct guesses
- **Animated Feedback**: Celebratory effects for correct answers
- **Responsive Design**: Play on any device
- **Interactive Background**: Particle.js animation effects
- **Instant Restart**: New game button for continuous play
- **Accessible UI**: Large touch-friendly buttons

🎮 How to Play
Observe the target color box

Click the color button that matches the target

Get instant feedback (correct/wrong)

Earn points for correct guesses

Use "New Game" button to reset

Try to beat your high score!

🔧 Technical Details
Tech Stack:

HTML5

CSS3 (Animations/Grid/Flexbox)

Vanilla JavaScript

Key Components:

Dynamic color generation

Score tracking system

Animation handlers

Responsive layout management

Color System
The game uses carefully selected colors from the HSL spectrum:

javascript
Copy
const predefinedColors = [
'#FF6B6B', '#4ECDC4', '#45B7D1',
'#96CEB4', '#FFEEAD', '#FF9999'
];
📚 Documentation
Game Attributes
data-testid="colorBox": Target color display

data-testid="colorOption": Color choice buttons

data-testid="score": Score display

data-testid="newGameButton": Reset button

Animation Types
Correct Guess:

Color box bounce

Wrong Guess:

Button shake

Red feedback text

